msgid ""
"The material used for these Tails workshops is available on our website in "
"[English](https://tails.net/contribute/how/promote/slides/"
"Ciclo_Autodefensa_Digital_202204/Tails-English.odp), [Spanish](https://tails."
"net/contribute/how/promote/slides/Ciclo_Autodefensa_Digital_202204/Tails-"
"Spanish.odp), and [Portuguese](https://tails.net/contribute/how/promote/"
"slides/Ciclo_Autodefensa_Digital_202204/Tails-Portuguese.odp)."
msgstr ""
"El material utilitzat per a aquests tallers de Tails està disponible al "
"nostre lloc web en [anglès](https://tails.net/contribute/how/promote/"
"material/slides/Ciclo_Autodefensa_Digital_202204/Tails-English.odp), "
